n-has-died-aged-65-3551301">在这里</a>找到来自娱乐界的许多其他致敬内容。</p><p> Pogues 的歌迷们正<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-rallying-to-get-the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-to-christmas-number-one-after-death-of-shane-macgowan-3551355">齐心协力，力争让《Fairytale of New York》登上今年圣诞节排行榜第一名的位置</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-re-enters-top-40-following-shane-macgowans-death-3552257">本周，这首歌重新进入了前 20 名</a>。</p><p>麦高恩的妹妹西沃恩也分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowans-sister-on-how-fairytale-of-new-york-captured-what-christmas-was-like-3552205">这首歌如何为很多人“捕捉到了圣诞节的感觉”</a> ，并补充道：“令我印象深刻的是，终于有一首圣诞歌曲比其他圣诞歌曲更能描绘现实生活。 ”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-u2-play-a-rainy-night-in-soho-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3552402">Watch U2 向 Shane MacGowan 致敬的后剧《A Rainy Night in Soho》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
